<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Jina la Yesu, Salamu!
 Lisujudieni,
 Ninyi Mbinguni, hukumu
 Na enzi mpeni.

[V2]
 Enzi na apewe kwetu,
 Watetea dini;
 Mkuzeni Bwana wenu,
 Na enzi mpeni.

[V3]
 Enyi mbegu ya rehema,
 Nanyi msifuni;
 Mmeponywa kwa neema,
 Na enzi mpeni.

[V4]
 Wenye dhambi kumbukeni
 Ya msalabani,
 Kwa furaha msifuni,
 Na enzi mpeni.

[V5]
 Kila mtu duniani
 Msujudieni,
 Kote-kote msifuni,
 Na enzi mpeni.

[V6]
 Sisi na wao pamoja
 Tu mumo sifani,
 Milele sifa ni moja,
 Ni 'Enzi mpeni.'</lyrics>
<title>Jina la Yesu, salamu! TZR4</title>
<hymn_number>4</hymn_number>
</song>